author: Alexandra Hutzler
title: Wisconsin Moves Forward With In-Person Elections Despite Coronavirus Stay At Home Order
description: The state has called in National Guard troops to staff polling sites, as thousands of workers are expected to not show up because of the coronavirus outbreak.
content:
Wisconsin is forging ahead with its statewide elections despite ordering residents to stay at home amid the coronavirus pandemic.
